title: BoardGameGeek Hotness
content:
1. **Brass: Pittsburgh**
*2026*
Take part in the United States' late 19th-century industrial boom.
![Brass: Pittsburgh](toplist_images/bgg_ea39e432.jpg)

2. **Dice Horde**
*2026*
Roll & Write meets Tower Defense!
![Dice Horde](toplist_images/bgg_2170ac63.jpg)

3. **The Old King's Crown**
*2025*
Out-manoeuvre your rivals as you vie for control of an ancient, crumbling kingdom.
![The Old King's Crown](toplist_images/bgg_639b48e4.jpg)

4. **Concordia**
*2013*
Merchants build and trade throughout the Roman Empire to please the Gods.
![Concordia](toplist_images/bgg_4002ad67.jpg)

5. **Magical Athlete**
*2025*
Pit a cast of crazy characters against each other in a madcap race to the finish.
![Magical Athlete](toplist_images/bgg_a8550ec2.png)

6. **Limit**
*2025*
Lead your nation in the world system.
![Limit](toplist_images/bgg_87845a0e.jpg)

7. **Labyrinth: Chronicles**
*2026*
New take on the all-time classic. Explore the 3D Labyrinth, and help the villagers!
![Labyrinth: Chronicles](toplist_images/bgg_6b8a600f.png)

8. **Tigris & Euphrates**
*1997*
Keep your Mesopotamian civilization in perfect balance through revolutions and wars.
![Tigris & Euphrates](toplist_images/bgg_6b4ff2dc.png)

9. **SETI: Search for Extraterrestrial Intelligence**
*2024*
Search for signs of alien life by launching probes and analyzing distant signals.
![SETI: Search for Extraterrestrial Intelligence](toplist_images/bgg_cdb80ee5.jpg)

10. **Almighty**
*2027*
Perform mighty acts upon hapless mortals to earn belief and glory.
![Almighty](toplist_images/bgg_b60852ef.png)

11. **Cozy Stickerville**
*2026*
Build your village with over 800 stickers! 
![Cozy Stickerville](toplist_images/bgg_08609c33.png)

12. **Nippon: Zaibatsu**
*2026*
Control conglomerates of companies driving Japan’s economy.
![Nippon: Zaibatsu](toplist_images/bgg_e707a5c7.png)

13. **Speakeasy**
*2025*
Earn money running a Manhattan speakeasy business during Prohibition.
![Speakeasy](toplist_images/bgg_171e42d9.jpg)

14. **The Lord of the Rings: Fate of the Fellowship**
*2025*
As members of The Fellowship, embark on a journey to save—or doom—Middle-earth.
![The Lord of the Rings: Fate of the Fellowship](toplist_images/bgg_805815e8.png)

15. **Brass: Birmingham**
*2018*
Build networks, grow industries, and navigate the world of the Industrial Revolution.
![Brass: Birmingham](toplist_images/bgg_517d2cbd.jpg)

16. **Eternal Decks**
*2025*
Can you solve each stage before your deck runs out?
![Eternal Decks](toplist_images/bgg_bffd55dd.png)

17. **Voidfall**
*2023*
Repel the Voidborn and restore Domineum in this space themed, heavy Euro.
![Voidfall](toplist_images/bgg_3b38a0f7.jpg)

18. **Ark Nova**
*2021*
Plan and build a modern, scientifically managed zoo to support conservation projects.
![Ark Nova](toplist_images/bgg_26067292.jpg)

19. **Inferno**
*2024*
Abandon Hope All Ye Who Enter Here.
![Inferno](toplist_images/bgg_47b43c86.jpg)

20. **Heat: Pedal to the Metal**
*2022*
Push your car to the limit in the pursuit of victory, but don’t overheat!
![Heat: Pedal to the Metal](toplist_images/bgg_cd1531b6.png)

21. **Mythologies**
*2026*
Draft legendary entities from ancient mythologies to your ever-evolving pantheon.
![Mythologies](toplist_images/bgg_fd481d23.jpg)

22. **Andromeda's Edge**
*2024*
Factions clash on the edge of the galaxy!
![Andromeda's Edge](toplist_images/bgg_8beeb14b.jpg)

23. **Galactic Cruise**
*2025*
Build and launch ships to send guests on luxurious space vacations.
![Galactic Cruise](toplist_images/bgg_8b1e71ae.jpg)

24. **Hot Streak**
*2025*
Which mascot will cross the finish line first? Who will be DQ'd?
![Hot Streak](toplist_images/bgg_4d2159ed.jpg)

25. **Corps of Discovery: A Game Set in the World of Manifest Destiny**
*2025*
Explore America and rid the land of the invasive monsters that have appeared.
![Corps of Discovery: A Game Set in the World of Manifest Destiny](toplist_images/bgg_925b06f4.jpg)
author: boardgamegeek.com
